- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper uses parameterized complexity theory to analyze the complexity of reasoning. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper deals with the representation and manipulation of knowledge, which is relevant to programming languages.
